# SauceDemo QA — Core

Playwright project for **SauceDemo** ([saucedemo.com](https://www.saucedemo.com/)) UI E2E tests.

**Playbook:** [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) · **Human overview:** [README.md](../../README.md) · **Test plan:** [docs/SAUCEDEMO_TEST_PLAN.md](../../docs/SAUCEDEMO_TEST_PLAN.md)

---

## Layout

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `tests/frontend/saucedemo/` | UI E2E (`chromium`) |
| `src/pages/saucedemo/` | POM |
| `src/fixtures/` | `fe-fixtures` |
| `src/data/input-data/` | Users, checkout data |
| `envs/` | `.env.local`, `.env.dev`, `.env.prod` |
| `reports/monocart-report-latest/` | Overwritten each run → `npm run generate-docs` |

Specs live in **`tests/`**; framework code in **`src/`**.

---

## Path aliases

| Alias | Path |
|-------|------|
| `@fixtures/*` | `src/fixtures/*` |
| `@pages/*` | `src/pages/*` |
| `@helpers/*` | `src/test-helpers/*` |
| `@config/*` | `src/config/*` |

Playwright config: **`src/config/playwright.config.ts`**

---

## Commands

```bash
npm run playwright -- tests/frontend/saucedemo --project=chromium
npm run playwright -- --grep @smoke
test_env=dev npm run playwright
npm run generate-docs
npm run tsc
npm run playwright:install
```

---

## Projects

| Project | `testDir` | Use |
|---------|-----------|-----|
| `chromium` | `tests/frontend` | SauceDemo UI |

Locale: `en-US`. `BASE_URL` → https://www.saucedemo.com/

